            <title>[PDFBOX-3657] Image rendering fails (1 bit per component image)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3657</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m trying to extract an image from a pdf. But somehow PDFBox makes  a mess with the image components. I&apos;ve attached the PDF page and the output image (Converted with PDFBox-PDFToImage 2.0.4) Perhaps there is a bug in the SampledImageReader?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
