&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3657&quot; title=&quot;Image rendering fails (1 bit per component image)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3657&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3657&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: 1-bit fast path only if numComponents is 1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15830187" author="tilman" created="Thu, 19 Jan 2017 16:21:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, thank you. I&apos;ve added an extra check that the 1-bit fast path is only to be used if numComponents is 1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
